==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Epagoge
<hw>Ep`a*go"ge</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L., from Gr.
<grk>'epagwgh`</grk> a bringing in, fr. <grk>'epa`gein</grk>. See
<er>Epact</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Logic)</fld> <def>The adducing of
particular examples so as to lead to a universal conclusion; the
argument by induction.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Epagogic</ent>⟦br⟧
